General.Name: Mighty Kingdom Ltd
General.Description: Mighty Kingdom Limited engages in the video game development business in Australia. The company develops video games for console, PC, and mobile platforms. Its games portfolio includes PETER RABBIT RUN!, AVA'S MANOR, GABBY'S DOLLHOUSE, CONAN CHOP CHOP, WILD LIFE, SHOPKINS, STAR TREK LOWER DECKS, and DANGER DAYS. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Adelaide, Australia.
